46@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0047@@</p></li></ul><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0048@@</p><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0049@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0050@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0051@@</p></li></ul><h1 id=\"h_72556480c6\">@@body:0052@@</h1><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0053@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0054@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0055@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0056@@</p></li></ul><h1 id=\"h_7388e8308b\">@@body:0057@@</h1><ol><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0058@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0059@@</p><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0060@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0061@@</p></li></ul></li></ol><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0062@@</p><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"h_4efd5ba372\">@@body:0063@@</h1><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0064@@</p><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0065@@</p><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container\"><img height=\"0\" src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.eu/i/o/nfttr45j/113348894/7b026ff17af9f90f183ff9bb3539/Screenshot+2026-03-06+at+15_56_19.png?expires=1781870400&amp;signature=7bc1245bfdb8eacb16d8a696ded028217ec1d88c98ea56126afa64efbfe12b7e&amp;req=0dRsxlzypD4slxv2%2Btxgpmif6vCzxfFDIMPIg1qs98Ecxqkxi%2F8q3LRiicf%2F%0AAcLPPGz54bKYNZo8YIyRixwF9Q%3D%3D%0A\" style=\"height: auto;\" width=\"2298\"/></div><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0066@@</p>",
  "segments": {
    "title": {
      "field": "title",
      "text": "What data can you export from your platform?",
      "hash": "30495b867bd8"
    },
    "description": {
      "field": "description",
      "text": "How to export the different types of data collected on the platform",
      "hash": "cf68e7a4852f"
    },
    "body:0001": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "What are data exports on the platform?",
      "hash": "b2775364e58c"
    },
    "body:0002": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "You can export most types of data from the platform to analyze participation, track activity, and generate reports.",
      "hash": "ff2e8ebe4acb"
    },
    "body:0003": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Exportable data includes:",
      "hash": "25728557f019"
    },
    "body:0004": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Invitation records</b>",
      "hash": "e61cc7aca439"
    },
    "body:0005": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>User registration details</b>",
      "hash": "77f47cf4beaf"
    },
    "body:0006": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Input (ideas, comments, statuses, tags)</b>",
      "hash": "36b24b88b992"
    },
    "body:0007": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Surveys and polls</b>",
      "hash": "4f5e677bfd21"
    },
    "body:0008": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Workshops</b> (polls, cards, conclusions — <b>not</b> chat)",
      "hash": "368e971da196"
    },
    "body:0009": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to export invitation data?",
      "hash": "41bf8a9a87f9"
    },
    "body:0010": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Go to <b>Invitations &gt; All Invitations</b>",
      "hash": "a4ae6546265f"
    },
    "body:0011": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Click <b>Export</b>",
      "hash": "7851874f7b79"
    },
    "body:0012": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "You’ll receive an Excel file with:",
      "hash": "2d5cc7c00f11"
    },
    "body:0013": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Email addresses",
      "hash": "6a2e6841d18e"
    },
    "body:0014": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Status",
      "hash": "920e413c7d41"
    },
    "body:0015": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Unique registration token",
      "hash": "6f0244d6d2f1"
    },
    "body:0016": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Assigned groups/roles (if any)",
      "hash": "a0759dfd0f60"
    },
    "body:0017": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Use this data to resend invites or track group-specific outreach efforts.",
      "hash": "869868283125"
    },
    "body:0018": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to export user data?",
      "hash": "489d6789ebee"
    },
    "body:0019": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Go to <b>Users</b> in the admin panel",
      "hash": "34d583413d5c"
    },
    "body:0020": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Choose to export:",
      "hash": "ce0dd7859212"
    },
    "body:0021": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "All users",
      "hash": "f7898130e557"
    },
    "body:0022": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "A specific group (manual or smart)",
      "hash": "8644a7ff6e61"
    },
    "body:0023": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "A custom selection",
      "hash": "f4846bec6d96"
    },
    "body:0024": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "The exported file will include:",
      "hash": "43b6ac29a7cd"
    },
    "body:0025": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "User ID",
      "hash": "7967e089a7b9"
    },
    "body:0026": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Name and email",
      "hash": "9024f54b7c45"
    },
    "body:0027": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Account creation date",
      "hash": "139250adb6c4"
    },
    "body:0028": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Profile link",
      "hash": "bdb5518e8c0f"
    },
    "body:0029": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Group memberships",
      "hash": "6ec54d702538"
    },
    "body:0030": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to export survey data?",
      "hash": "f3ee98b3602c"
    },
    "body:0031": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Go to the <b>Poll</b> or <b>Survey</b> phase in your project",
      "hash": "0ad35f32ec00"
    },
    "body:0032": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Go to the <b>Insights</b> tab",
      "hash": "e8f6b664d05f"
    },
    "body:0033": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Click <b>the 3 dots</b> on the left and select <b>‘Download survey results’</b>",
      "hash": "5e383bf1d538"
    },
    "body:0034": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Notes:",
      "hash": "da4f7ea58d96"
    },
    "body:0035": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Survey export options may depend on the survey tool used (Typeform, Google Forms, or in-platform survey).",
      "hash": "38fae753824f"
    },
    "body:0036": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Currently, you can’t export multiple polls across projects in one batch.<br/>AI Analysis tags applied to survey responses are not included in the export (tags are exported only for ideas, not for surveys).",
      "hash": "b66bfb40207e"
    },
    "body:0037": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to export ideas?",
      "hash": "dcec71e22de5"
    },
    "body:0038": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Go to a project’s <b>Input Manager</b> tab.",
      "hash": "42117427ecfd"
    },
    "body:0039": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Click <b>Export &gt; Export all ideas of this project</b> or select individual ideas.",
      "hash": "48b55f22cba0"
    },
    "body:0040": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "The Excel file will include:",
      "hash": "84e50561ba30"
    },
    "body:0041": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Title and description",
      "hash": "679d5af5537a"
    },
    "body:0042": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Author name, email, and user ID",
      "hash": "a5ce6386d285"
    },
    "body:0043": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Upvotes/downvotes/comments count",
      "hash": "1e06b2a145b9"
    },
    "body:0044": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Publication date",
      "hash": "29473cdce82e"
    },
    "body:0045": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Input status and tags",
      "hash": "000c0a1fdb91"
    },
    "body:0046": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "URL to the input",
      "hash": "acea2d9e0edb"
    },
    "body:0047": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Link to each attachment</b> (see limitations)",
      "hash": "cbaac0b9925d"
    },
    "body:0048": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Limitations:</b>",
      "hash": "af1b0e97da34"
    },
    "body:0049": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Images cannot be exported</b>.",
      "hash": "e0e63d78a747"
    },
    "body:0050": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Attachments are <b>linked</b>, not batched, each must be downloaded individually.",
      "hash": "7177076b6f7a"
    },
    "body:0051": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Only public comments are included (not admin/internal comments or feedback)",
      "hash": "b3703ef7c48e"
    },
    "body:0052": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to export attachments from ideas?",
      "hash": "c75d2c19b286"
    },
    "body:0053": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Export ideas following the steps above - you will therefore have a full excel files of ideas/comments. One of the columns will be called \"attachements\" this is where the link to the attachment can be found.",
      "hash": "f63fead6e7f5"
    },
    "body:0054": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Each attachment has its own download link, batch downloading is not supported.",
      "hash": "7ea563be637d"
    },
    "body:0055": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Images embedded in idea descriptions or comments are <b>not exportable</b>.",
      "hash": "4b1f128b31cb"
    },
    "body:0056": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "The export also includes useful details such as title, description, author info, publication date, metrics, tags, and status.",
      "hash": "63ba62caca63"
    },
    "body:0057": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to export workshop results?",
      "hash": "a5541d91ce36"
    },
    "body:0058": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "After the workshop is complete, click <b>Export Data</b>.",
      "hash": "0882ab9086fd"
    },
    "body:0059": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "An Excel file is generated with:",
      "hash": "90b807c12dc0"
    },
    "body:0060": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Separate sheets for each workshop step",
      "hash": "1d332d62da06"
    },
    "body:0061": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Participant inputs from each activity",
      "hash": "2921dfc2f7e3"
    },
    "body:0062": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Note:</b> Workshop <b>chat</b> messages are <b>not</b> exportable due to privacy and data formatting limitations.",
      "hash": "d61de4712470"
    },
    "body:0063": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Using the API to export all other data",
      "hash": "aec00cdce415"
    },
    "body:0064": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "For other data that cannot be easily downloaded from the platform, you are able to use our public API to pull all types of data from the platform and use it for external data analysis. For example to download things like a master list of all projects on the platform (like project names, dates, status) with the API you can easily pull such a list.",
      "hash": "956da72109dd"
    },
    "body:0065": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "All API documentation can be found here: <a class=\"intercom-content-link\" href=\"https://developers.govocal.com/api/\" target=\"_blank\">https://developers.govocal.com/api/</a>. There you can see all the information that you can pull with the API. For example for projects you can see all the data attributes that you can pull:",
      "hash": "c94eaf75708f"
    },
    "body:0066": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<a class=\"intercom-content-link\" href=\"https://support.govocal.com/en/articles/527578-use-govocal-data-in-powerbi\" target=\"_blank\">Read more about using the API to pull data into PowerBI here</a>",
      "hash": "4bb23422ae72"
    }
  }
}